Package: slMSE
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the Simulation, Assessment and MSE for Short-Lived Species.  
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Tom", "Carruthers",
      email = "tom@bluematterscience.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: support a scientific process that begins with a collection of available data and information, 
    leads to the consolidation of those in a range of plausible scenarios for system dynamics, 
    this followed by a defensible assessment of the resource, and finally the development and potentially 
    adoption of management procedures that are demonstrably robust to scientific and management uncertainties.
